<item>
            <title>[SPARK-23643] XORShiftRandom.hashSeed allocates unnecessary memory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-23643</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The hashSeed method allocates 64 bytes buffer and puts only 8 bytes of the seed parameter into it. Other bytes are always zero and could be easily excluded from hash calculation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
